data.description:
Sweet and comfy home with enough room for you to make it yours. 2 bed/1 full bath+spacious den area that can be used as a 3rd bedroom or can be used just for extra living space. Formal dining area. Spacious kitchen area. 
The yard and garage/shop will blow you away with this home sitting on almost 1 acre. Garage is 2 car garage+space along the backside for a hobby space/work area. Come make this home your own.
